    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【游戏简述】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    《凡朽之躯：生存重筑》是一款融合了开放世界、沙盒生存和角色扮演等元素的科幻冒险游戏。故事发生在未来，技术迅速发展之际，生物工程和人工智能的进步使人类面临深刻的生存挑战与道德困境。玩家将探索一个充满未知的神秘岛屿，通过探索和搜集资源，制造装备，捕获AI仆从，与各个派系遭遇，不断改造强大自己来面对越来越强大的敌人，逐步解开背后的谜团。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【人体改造】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    玩家可通过探索获取材料，升级或修复体内植入的人体改造模块，从而获得全新特性或提升属性，使自己变得更加强大。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124330/extras/175146575830d0d17309f2ed7ae36751.avif?t=1732557322\" width=550 height=325 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124330/extras/716fd7d7b3ea35a2a8d56a444d6b2dc9.avif?t=1732557322\" width=550 height=413 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【机器人仆从】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 玩家通过挑战敌人或收集各类机器人残骸，修复后将其转化为自己的随从。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【派系】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏中存在众多大小派系，玩家可以探索其背后的故事，获取他们的科技或装备，享受丰富的选择与体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【丰富的武器与装备】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中包含超过160种武器和物品，供玩家收集和制作。多样的武器和装备为玩家提供了丰富的战斗选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124330/extras/b576de0daf72b859d16541be4d96c494.avif?t=1732557322\" width=550 height=536 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【完全动态的气候与环境交互】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏拥有四季变化、动态天气和高自由度的环境交互，玩家可通过地形改造或自定义季节植被色彩，随心所欲的塑造游戏世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124330/extras/1e63b9baaa9d5de08ba0f6a529020c65.poster.avif?t=1732557322\" width=550 height=309 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124330/extras/1e63b9baaa9d5de08ba0f6a529020c65.webm?t=1732557322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【有深度的四季循环】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四季变化不仅仅是视觉体验，还蕴含更深的内涵。每个循环带来独特的挑战与策略，为玩家提供多样化的玩法与冒险。每一次循环都是一次挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【沙盒生存】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合沙盒生存游戏的经典元素，提供高度自由、开放的游戏方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124330/extras/9d36df32e5d87066919465fb8f22f42b.poster.avif?t=1732557322\" width=550 height=309 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124330/extras/9d36df32e5d87066919465fb8f22f42b.webm?t=1732557322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>提示</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >：<i>游戏仍在开发中。当前展示的美术元素、风格和功能可能会发生变化。后期会对美术和细节做更换或提升。感谢您的理解和支持！</i></p>",
